title: Interstellar comet 3I/ATLAS survived its flyby of the sun — and gave up some secrets in the process
description: Interstellar comets are the original cosmic explorers, and by studying their metallic whispers, we are learning the secrets of worlds we may never see directly.
content: Interstellar comets are the original cosmic explorers, and by studying their metallic whispers, we are learning the secrets of worlds we may never see directly.
